original_title: The Killers - Live At Pinkpop Festival
overview: The Killers perform at Pinkpop Festival from Landgraaf, Netherlands on May 30, 2009 from the Day & Age Tour. SetList: Human Somebody Told Me For Reasons Unknown Losing Touch Bones Bling (Confession of a King) Shadowplay (Joy Division cover) Smile Like You Mean It Spaceman A Dustland Fairytale Sam's Town Read My Mind Mr. Brightside All These Things That I've Done Jenny Was A Friend Of Mine When You Were Young
title: The Killers - Live At Pinkpop Festival
